===Etymology===
From [[w:Epistle to the Galatians|Galatians]] 6:7 in the [[Bible]] ([[King James Version]]; spelling modernized): “Be not deceived, God is not mocked: for whatsoever a man soweth, that shall he also reap.”<ref>{{R:King James Version|Galatians|6|7|page=1429|column=2|passage=Be not deceiued, God is not mocked: for whatſoeuer a man ſoweth, that ſhall he alſo reape.|nodot=1}}</ref>

